{
  "stem": "25773.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this army, military-- and we were scared, scared, scared to death-- the two of us, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Krystyna disappeared because she was with her family, and we working in the kitchens.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then Stefan appears also, because through the pharmacy, he came to-- was taken to Pruszkow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He went to the pharmacy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He-- he knew where we were because we left the dress.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He came after you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he came to us, to meet us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And once or twice we had a scare because there were some people, musicians, who were in band.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, there were a lot of musicians in Poland, and they mixed [INAUDIBLE] the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they thought [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Masia ?] and I, and we were a bit scared.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But Stefan said, they are already losing their war, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And indeed, you see, one day-- and it was-- we were one day-- one year, and more and more and more refugees came from Warsaw, and young people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had a very, very jolly time at times, apart from hard work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we supported Stefan.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Whenever we went to the [INAUDIBLE] to cook, we had aprons with the-- with the-- with the big pockets inside, so whenever we cut a piece of sausage, cut a piece of meat, cut a piece of that-- right in.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we came home, we fed Stefan, because Stefan was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He cooked for himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we went--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, then-- then the lady, or the farmer's wife, was a very fine and very nice lady.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the farmer himself was really a gentleman, a Polish gentleman.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Polish farmer gentleman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was not a peasant, he was a farmer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He owed a lot of land.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
